---
title: Homestyle Meatloaf with Shallot Gravy & Caramelized Root Vegetables
description: It might not be your mom's recipe, but we promise this homey dish will bring back major memories. Flavored with mild shallot and woodsy thyme, our meatloaf packs sophisticated flavor and serious tenderness. Of course, the dish wouldn't be complete without a generous smothering of homemade gravy. Who's hungry?
